Description
===========
This a counter app for counting different subjects.
the app provides creating new counter, edit oldcounter, listing the old counters
and conclude the counter status.


usage
=====
when the user starts the app there will be a loading screen.
the second activity is laying out the main manue, which has two buttons. One is for
creating new counter activity and the second button is to list all the old counters
that user has made.
for creating new counter acitivity, user can create a new counter by typing a counter 
name in the widget. Once there is a duplication, the app will pop an toast, saying "duplicate counter".
After the user create a new counter the following activity is to let the user manipulate the counter.
"add, reset, rename, and counter detail" are options to edit the counter.
for the listing all the counter activity, the user can check all the old counter and user can choose one
counter to edit by simple click on the counter name.
Also if the user want to DELETE the a certain counter the user just needs to long press on the counter 
and the counter will be deleted.
